<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=El_Lissitzky&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span class="citation book">Albrecht, Wilma Ruth: (1993). <i>EL - wie Lissitzky. Das Künstlerporträt</i><i>. Liberal, 35 (1993) 4, pp. 50-60. ISSN 0459-1992.</i></span></li>
